DashboardDefinitionComponents.Name: Actual, Leaves and Holiday Hours
DashboardDefinitionComponents.Parameters:
[{"WidgetSubTitle":"Actual, Leaves and Holiday Hours","WidgetType":"chart","WidgetFilterField":"","WidgetColor":"#efefef","WidgetFrameStyle":{},"WidgetXPosition":22,"WidgetYPosition":0,"WidgetRows":7,"WidgetColumns":26,"WidgetHeader":{"showTitle":true,"showSubTitle":false,"WidgetMetrics":{"visible":false,"Metrics":[]},"WidgetPeriodChooser":{"visible":false,"type":"","startDate":null,"endDate":null}},"WidgetDataSources":{"main":{"type":"querytext","value":"SELECT	SUM(v.ActualHours) as ActualHours,
		SUM(v.LeaveHours) as LeaveHours,
		SUM(v.HolidayHours) as HolidayHours,
		v.[Month]
FROM	(
		SELECT 	SUM(v.ActualTime) as ActualHours,
				0 as LeaveHours,
				0 as HolidayHours,
				DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 1) as [Month]
		FROM	Analytics.Timesheet(@CurrentUserId) v
		WHERE	v.[Date] between @FromDate and @ToDate and 
                v.CompanyId = @CompanyOid and
                (@ClientGroupOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' or v.ClientGroupId = @ClientGroupOid)
		GROUP BY DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 1)
		UNION ALL
		SELECT 	0 as ActualHours,
				SUM(v.[Hours]) as LeaveHours,
				0 as HolidayHours,
				DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 1) as [Month]
		FROM	Analytics.Leave(@CurrentUserId) v
		WHERE	v.[Date] between @FromDate and @ToDate and 
                v.CompanyId = @CompanyOid
		GROUP BY DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 1)
		UNION ALL
		SELECT 	0 as ActualHours,
				0 as LeaveHours,
				SUM(v.[Hours]) as HolidayHours,
				DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 1) as [Month]
		FROM	Analytics.Holiday(@CurrentUserId) v
		WHERE	v.[Date] between @FromDate and @ToDate and 
                v.CompanyId = @CompanyOid
		GROUP BY DATEFROMPARTS(v.[Year], v.[Month], 1)
) v
GROUP BY v.[Month]","mapping":""}},"Filters":{},"QueryConfiguration":{"PreviousPeriod":{"Show":false,"KeyFieldName":"","Type":0},"RequiredFilters":["CompanyOid","ClientGroupOid","FromDate","ToDate"]}}]

DashboardDefinitionComponents.Name: Company and Client Group
Deliverables Staffing
DashboardDefinitionComponents.Parameters:
[{"WidgetSubTitle":"Hours and Fee per Typology Group","WidgetType":"pivotgrid","WidgetFilterField":"","WidgetColor":"#efefef","WidgetFrameStyle":{},"WidgetXPosition":0,"WidgetYPosition":7,"WidgetRows":23,"WidgetColumns":48,"WidgetHeader":{"showContextInfo":false,"WidgetPeriodChooser":{"type":"year","visible":false},"WidgetMetrics":{"visible":false,"Metrics":[]},"showSubTitle":true,"showTitle":true},"WidgetDataSources":{"main":{"type":"querytext","value":"select  IIF(eit.[Order] < 10, concat('0', eit.[Order], '. ', eit.[Description]), concat(eit.[Order], '. ', eit.[Description])) as Deliverable,
        art.[Name] as [Service],
        utg.[Name] as TypologyGroup,
        usr.[Name] as [User],
		div.[Name] as Division,
        dep.[Name] as Department,
        edt.[Hours] as ContractedTime,
		cg.[Name] as ClientGroup,
		cc.[Name] as ClientName,
		c.[Name] as FeeProposal,
		est.[Name] as EstimateName,
		IIF(n.RoleId is not null, edt.UnitPriceCost, null) as Rate,
		IIF(n.RoleId is not null, edt.[Rate], null) as TableRate,
        edt.ValueWithoutVatIncome as TotalDeliverable,
		IIF(n.RoleId is not null, edt.UnitPriceCost * edt.[Hours], null) as Total,
		cast(est.[Date] as Date) as StartDate,
		cast(est.[Expiration] as Date) as EndDate
from    Estimate est	left outer join CommercialClient cc on cc.Oid = est.Client
						left outer join [Contract] c on c.Oid = est.[Contract]
						left outer join ClientGroup cg on cg.Oid = cc.ClientGroup,
						
		EstimateItem eit, 
		Article art,
        EstimateItemDetail edt	left outer join Department dep on dep.Oid = edt.Department
								left outer join Division div on div.Oid = dep.Division
								left outer join [User] usr on usr.Oid = edt.[User]
								left outer join UserTypologyGroup utg on utg.Oid = edt.UserTypologyGroup
								left outer join Analytics.[Authorization](@CurrentUserId) n on (n.RoleName = 'RateCardRead')
where   eit.Estimate = est.Oid and
        edt.EstimateItem = eit.Oid and
        edt.[Type] = 2 and
        art.Oid = eit.Article and 
        est.[Date] between @FromDate and @ToDate and
		(cg.Oid = @ClientGroupOid or @ClientGroupOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000') and
		(utg.Company = @CompanyOid or @CompanyOid = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000')
order by eit.[Order]","mapping":""}},"Filters":{},"QueryConfiguration":{"RequiredFilters":["CompanyOid","ClientGroupOid","FromDate","ToDate"]}}]
